msgid "For regular plain requests (not chrome based), maximum number of seconds until timeout, 1-999."
msgstr "Pour les requêtes simples (sans Chrome), délai d'expiration maximum en secondes (1-999)."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings.html
msgid "Applied to all requests."
msgstr "Appliqué à toutes les requêtes."

