msgctxt "AI usage stats"
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Utilisation"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Aperçu"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "Provider"
msgstr "Fournisseur"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "Prompts"
msgstr "Prompts (Instructions)"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "Behaviour"
msgstr "Comportement"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "AI-powered change monitoring"
msgstr "Surveillance des changements par IA"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "Connect an LLM to move from \"something changed\" to \"only the thing you care about changed\"."
msgstr "Connectez un LLM pour passer de \"quelque chose a changé\" à \"ce qui m'intéresse a changé\"."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "Intent filtering"
msgstr "Filtrage par intention"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Each watch or tag can carry a plain-text intent — %(ex1)s or %(ex2)s. On every detected change the AI evaluates the "
"diff against it and suppresses irrelevant noise."
msgstr ""
"Chaque surveillance peut avoir une intention en texte clair — %(ex1)s ou %(ex2)s. À chaque changement, l'IA "
"évalue le diff et supprime le bruit non pertinent."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Instead of raw diffs, receive plain-language summaries in notifications — %(ex1)s or %(ex2)s. Set a global default "
"prompt here, or override per watch or tag."
msgstr ""
"Au lieu de diffs bruts, recevez des résumés clairs — %(ex1)s ou %(ex2)s. Définissez un prompt par défaut "
"ici ou personnalisez-le par surveillance."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "Minimal cost"
msgstr "Coût minimal"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The AI sees only a unified diff of what changed — never full page HTML. Low-cost models like %(gpt)s or %(gemini)s "
"handle this well, typically fractions of a cent per check."
msgstr ""
"L'IA ne voit que le diff unifié, jamais le HTML complet. Des modèles économiques comme %(gpt)s ou %(gemini)s "
"gèrent cela pour quelques fractions de centime par vérification."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "AI / LLM configured:"
msgstr "IA / LLM configuré :"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "Configure AI Provider"
msgstr "Configurer le fournisseur IA"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "AI Provider"
msgstr "Fournisseur IA"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "Third-party data transfer — please read"
msgstr "Transfert de données tiers — veuillez lire attentivement"

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid ""
"When AI features are active, change data from the websites you monitor — including page diffs and extracted text — is"
" sent to an external AI provider of your choice."
msgstr ""
"Quand l'IA est active, les données de changement (diffs, texte extrait) sont envoyées au fournisseur IA externe choisi."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "You are solely responsible for ensuring this complies with the terms of service of each website you monitor."
msgstr "Vous êtes seul responsable de la conformité avec les conditions d'utilisation des sites surveillés."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid ""
"You are solely responsible for compliance with applicable data-protection laws (e.g. GDPR) regarding any personal "
"data that may appear in monitored content."
msgstr ""
"Vous êtes seul responsable du respect des lois sur la protection des données (ex: RGPD) pour toute donnée personnelle "
"présente dans le contenu surveillé."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid ""
"API costs charged by your chosen provider are your own responsibility; this software has no visibility into or "
"control over those charges."
msgstr ""
"Les coûts d'API facturés par votre fournisseur sont à votre charge ; ce logiciel n'a aucun contrôle sur ces frais."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid ""
"AI / LLM models are known to hallucinate — producing plausible-sounding but factually incorrect or entirely "
"fabricated output with apparent confidence — and by design may omit or truncate relevant data during summarisation. "
"AI output must never be relied upon as complete or accurate. This software is provided as-is with no warranty of any "
"kind."
msgstr ""
"Les modèles d'IA peuvent halluciner (produire des faits faux avec assurance) ou omettre des données importantes. "
"Le contenu généré par l'IA ne doit jamais être considéré comme complet ou exact. Ce logiciel est fourni tel quel."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid ""
"By enabling AI features you personally indemnify and hold harmless the creator(s) and contributor(s) of this software"
" from any claims, damages, or liability arising from this data transfer or your use of AI features."
msgstr ""
"En activant l'IA, vous dégagez les créateurs du logiciel de toute responsabilité concernant le transfert de données "
"ou l'usage des fonctionnalités d'IA."

#: changedetectionio/blueprint/settings/templates/settings_llm_tab.html
msgid "I have read and understood the above."
msgstr "J'ai lu et compris ce qui précède."